q_en: What is the material with the highest remaining inventory?

steps.sql: SELECT m.id, m.name FROM warehouse_material wm JOIN materials m ON wm.material_id = m.id ORDER BY wm.left_number DESC LIMIT 1;
steps.description: Retrieve the material ID and name with the highest remaining inventory from the warehouse_material table

response:
Sure thing! Based on the latest data, the material with the highest remaining inventory is:

| Material ID | Material Name |
|-------------|---------------|
| 6           | Silk Pieces   |
